    <item>
      <title>习近平的含混信息让投资者对中国保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/xi-s-mixed-messages-leave-whiplashed-investors-wary-of-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，习近平主席一直在努力吸引外资，同时继续重塑中国的营商环境，以确保他的权力在国内外都不会受到挑战。这些有时相互冲突的目标让投资者感到困惑，也让官僚们感到紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/xi-s-mixed-messages-leave-whiplashed-investors-wary-of-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
